        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Oscillogram and spectrogram of Melanophryniscus cambaraensis call from FLONA SFP (A - FZ 9093) and a close view of the call (B); and a close view of the call of M. macrogranulosus from Garapiá (C – FZ9102) and from Morro da Gruta (D – FZ 9113). In each figure we show call part A (single pulses) and B (pulsed trill) of the call." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4315659/files/figure.png" .

